de.esoco.lib.property

Class StandardProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.esoco.lib.property.StandardProperties

  • public class StandardProperties
extends java.lang.Object
    This class defines several standard property names. Whenever possible these property names should be preferred over self-defined ones because they allow to access common properties in a generic way.
